{"tid":164162,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"學民思潮捐款=黃之鋒私己錢","createTime":"2017-03-20T13:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T23:24:42.000Z","uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d667877a68f2f919d7a8587e1537d54ec8c53342","tid":164162,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:15:46.000Z","msg":"【「學民思潮法律援助基金」2016-17年度財政匯報】<br />\n<br />\n學民思潮已按照2016年3月20日所公佈之財政安排*，撥款港幣七十五萬元正予鄧王周廖成利律師行管理的「學民思潮法律援助基金」，以支援所有任職學民思潮成員期間，參與行動後所面臨的官司、審訊和檢控所須律師費用。 <br />\n<br />\n基金現由六名受託人（黃之鋒、黃子悅、周庭、許樂絲、陳寶玲、鍾禮謙）負責審批，並將每年公開核數報告及個案性質。 基金受託人於2016年12月24日通過動議，撥出港幣三十二萬五千元正予 &ldquo;Vidler &amp; Co Solicitors&rdquo;（韋智達律師行和石書銘大律師），以支付成員黃之鋒於中聯辦燒白皮書案被控阻礙公職人員執行職務（案件編號: ESCC2219/2015）的法律訴訟費用。<br />\n<br />\n故此，「學民思潮法律援助基金」現時尚餘款項為港幣四十二萬五千元正。「學民思潮法律援助基金」之詳細核數報告將待稍後公佈。特此聲明。<br />\n<br />\n「學民思潮法律援助基金」受託人（黃之鋒、黃子悅、周庭、許樂絲、陳寶玲、鍾禮謙） 謹啟<br />\n<br />\n二零一七年三月二十日<br />\n<br />\n*<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Scholarism/photos/a.217979064901174.59816.211662168866197/1129251990440539/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FScholarism%2Fphotos%2Fa.217979064901174.59816.211662168866197%2F1129251990440539%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=afebb296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Scholarism/photos/a.217979064901174.59816.211662168866197/1129251990440539/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1455268094505592&amp;id=211662168866197\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1455268094505592%26id%3D211662168866197&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=63680986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1455268094505592&amp;id=211662168866197</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a05f90e5e5ce7ed7222b9f1fdb3cec3d619f4c","tid":164162,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">基金受託人於2016年12月24日通過動議，撥出港幣三十二萬五千元正予 &ldquo;Vidler &amp; Co Solicitors&rdquo;（韋智達律師行和石書銘大律師），以支付成員黃之鋒於中聯辦燒白皮書案被控阻礙公職人員執行職務（案件編號: ESCC2219/2015）的法律訴訟費用。<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"86dba35197ee52752511a445b139da050ef28a6e","tid":164162,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"財技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ce03f5bf96959c8d37af86a2b5760d4e850610","tid":164162,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒：「今晚食清啲！」"},{"pid":"b653af2c6e1f39b4602595be6d49e2d753958496","tid":164162,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865bdad7457a81406da40997ccf2d4f9525c2955","tid":164162,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T22:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35aa6c465086b47a9b8f3426a6d8d3543ce444d3","tid":164162,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T23:24:42.000Z","msg":"唔係宜家先知阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}